<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Classic Literature Summaries</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
<h1>Classic Literature Summaries</h1>

<p>Welcome to our website, where you can find summaries of some of the most prominent classic literature works.
Our summaries are autogenerated by <a href="https://chat.openai.com/chat">ChatGPT</a>, and are organized by genre for your convenience.</p>

<h2>Genres</h2>
  <table>
    {% for genre in genres %}
    <tr>
      <td class="genre-name"><a href="{{ genre.genre|lower }}.html">{{ genre.genre }}</a></td>
      <td>{{ genre.description }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </table>

<p>Explore the works in each genre by clicking on the links above. Please note that our summaries are autogenerated and may contain inaccuracies or spoilers. We do not allow user contributions at this time.</p>

<h2>Featured Works</h2>

<p>Here are some of our featured works:</p>

<ul>
  {% for work in featured_works %}
    <li><a href="{{ work.url }}"><em>{{ work.title }}</em> by {{ work.author }} {% if work.publication_year < 0 %}
  ({{ -work.publication_year }} B.C.)
{% else %}
  ({{ work.publication_year }})
{% endif %}
</a></li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>

<p>Check out these and many other classic literature works on our website!</p>  
</body>
</html>
